\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f\u9472\'3f}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af9\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\sl276\slmult1\sb140\sa120\keepn{\rtlch\af6\afs24\alang1081\ai0\ab0 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af5\loch\cf0\fs24\lang1031\i0\b0\kerning1\f5\dbch\af7\langfe2052\loch
In this video, I\u8217\'92ll be introducing the changes to the }{\rtlch\af6\afs24\alang1081\ai0\ab \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af5\loch\cs16\rtlch\ai \ltrch\loch\i\cf0\fs24\lang1031\i0\b0\kerning1\f5\dbch\af7\langfe2052\loch
Swarm Host}{\rtlch\af6\afs24\alang1081\ai0\ab0 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af5\loch\cf0\fs24\lang1031\i0\b0\kerning1\f5\dbch\af7\langfe2052\loch
.}
\par \pard\plain \s18\rtlch\af9\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\sl276\slmult1\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\sb0\sa140\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\sl276\slmult1{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab0 \ltrch\loch\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
The Swarm Host has long become just a }{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab \ltrch\loch\cs16\rtlch\ai \ltrch\loch\i\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
harassment unit}{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab0 \ltrch\loch\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
 that you rarely see anymore.\line In addition, }{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab \ltrch\loch\cs16\rtlch\ai \ltrch\loch\i\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
Locusts block the movement of enemy units}{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab0 \ltrch\loch\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
 and prevent them from reaching the unit that spawned them. The same is true for }{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab \ltrch\loch\cs16\rtlch\ai \ltrch\loch\i\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
Broodlings}{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab0 \ltrch\loch\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
and even there it\u8217\'92s already quite strong, but at least Broodlings are }{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab \ltrch\loch\cs16\rtlch\ai \ltrch\loch\i\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
melee units and have less life}{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab0 \ltrch\loch\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
which means that in large numbers they usually deal }{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab \ltrch\loch\cs16\rtlch\ai \ltrch\loch\i\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
less effective damage}{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab0 \ltrch\loch\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
 because of limited space, and more importantly, they are }{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab \ltrch\loch\cs16\rtlch\ai \ltrch\loch\i\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
much easier to kill. And because }{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab0 \ltrch\loch\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
Locusts and Broodlings }{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab \ltrch\loch\cs16\rtlch\ai \ltrch\loch\i\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
cannot attack air units they are even more similiar. }
\par \pard\plain \s18\rtlch\af9\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\sl276\slmult1\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\sb0\sa140\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\sl276\slmult1{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab0 \ltrch\loch\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
That\u8217\'92s why in }{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab \ltrch\loch\cs16\rtlch\ai \ltrch\loch\i\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
sc2YouWantLocusts are now always flying}{\rtlch\af6\ai0\ab0 \ltrch\loch\i0\b0\dbch\af7\loch
