In this video, I present the changes made to the Ultralisk.}
\par \pard\plain \s19\rtlch\af9\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\sl276\slmult1\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\sb0\sa140\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\sl276\slmult1{\loch
In addition to the standard adjustments like increased health and reduced vision range, the Ultralisk now deals a lot more damage against structures, and Frenzy has been removed. Since there are no longer any Marauders with Concussive Shells to slow units, Fungal Growth no longer slows, and abilities like Anti-Armor Missile and Neural Parasite have been removed, the only remaining effects that can slow or stun Ultralisks are the reworked Hunter Seeker Missile, the Protoss Obelisk, and the Stasis Ward from the Oracle. These abilities are now specifically designed to counter or affect Ultralisks. Moreover, abilities like Time Warp, which now speeds up units instead of slowing them down, actually have a positive effect on the Ultralisk.}
\par \pard\plain \s19\rtlch\af9\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\sl276\slmult1\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\sb0\sa140\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af6\langfe2052\sl276\slmult1{\loch
Overall, the Ultralisk now has slightly more counters that can slow or stun it and is somewhat more effective against structures.}
